Pique: &quot;I am and I feel Catalan. Today I am more proud of people of Catalonia, despite the violence they have been more peaceful than ever.&quot;<br />
<br />
Pique: &quot;We (Catalans) are not a minority, we were millions of people. We are not bad people, we just want to vote&quot;

